<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.7">
<l>tīmaṉattāṉ kañcaṉatu vañcaṉaiyil tiriyun tēṉukaṉum pūtaṉaita ṉāruyiruñ cekuttāṉ</l>
<l>kāmaṉaittāṉ payantakaru mēṉiyuṭai yammāṉ karutumiṭam porutupuṉal tuṟaituṟaimut tunti</l>
<l>nāmaṉattāl mantiraṅkaḷ nālvēta maintu vēḷviyō ṭāṟaṅkam naviṉṟukalai payiṉṟaṅ</l>
<l>kāmaṉattu maṟaiyavarkaḷ payilumaṇi nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship there in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in lovely Nānkūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">[its] crashing waters casting up pearls at every ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent">where Vedic experts with proper minds train there,</l>
<l>Learning, with [their] minds and mouths, mantras, the four Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">the five sacrifices, and the six branches [of knowledge],</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] practicing [these Vedic] sciences,</l>
<l>The place where is manifest the dark-bodied lord who begot Kāma,</l>
<l>The one who destroyed the dear lives of Denuka and Pūtanā,</l>
<l rend="indent">who were entangled in the deceit of evil-minded Kaṁsa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
